revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Thing_Deactivate}}
{{Special|131|tid|Thing|Deactivate}}
* ''tid'': Thing ID of the thing to deactivate. 0 refers to the activator of the script.

Sets the {{Flag|DORMANT}} flag of a monster so that it will not be able to take damage or attack the player. Does nothing when used on players. Also, makes the actor call its <code>Deactivate()</code> [[ZScript virtual functions|virtual function]] (which does nothing by default, unless overridden to add custom behavior). This function does not interact with the {{property|Activation}} property. Details can be found on the '''[[Activation]]''' page.

